::Prowl::

Prowl frowns, looking back at Hot Rod. "Optimus Prime back?"

He frowns. There was something he was supposed to be able to 
remember, but what? It was something, something about Optimus Prime. 
He knew it! He knew he knew it. But he couldn't remember!

Prowl looks ahead of him, continuing to walk.
